      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "All existing tools are RETROSPECTIVE:\n\"Your code has a bug\" → \"Your service is down\"\n\nNobody owns the space between CODE and INFRA where:\n→ AI recommends WHAT to fix before you ship\n→ Micro-chaos validates resilience in staging\n→ Failure patterns become proactive playbooks\n\nThis is unexplored territory — and it's the gap\nbetween \"it passed tests\" and \"it won't fail in prod.\"",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10
    },

