      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 92,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "① Ship Resilience Agent v0.1\n   (micro-chaos + scoring, k8s sidecar)\n\n② Post 3 YouTube videos on methodology\n\n③ Get 5 design partners\n   (Worldline + 4 external startups)\n\n④ Open-source core + community\n\n⑤ Paid tier: AI Recommender Engine\n   (needs customer failure data first)\n\nValidate before building more.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10
    },

