      "versionNonce": 102,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "⚠ CodRabitt / Qodo could expand here\n   → They focus on CODE layer. Different swim lane.\n\n⚠ Broad AIOps platforms consolidating (Transposit shut down)\n   → Niche positioning is safer than broad platform play.\n\n⚠ Prediction without data = gimmick\n   → \"Recommend\" is honest, \"predict\" triggers proof demand.\n\n✓ Our speed: ship fast, iterate, niche down.\n✓ Worldline relationship = real feedback loop, not vanity.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10
    },

